<div class='media__message'>
<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>페이션스 므툰지(Patience Mthunzi)</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/patience_mthunzi_could_we_cure_hiv_with_lasers?language=ko' lang='ko'>
레이저로 HIV를 치료할 수 있을까요?
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
Aug 2015
</span>
</span>
<span class='meta__row'>
Rated
<span class='meta__val'>
Informative, Fascinating
</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
